          "severity": "high",
          "category": "security",
          "message": "The patch removes the admin/owner membership check (getEventTypeIdsWhereUserIsAdminOrOwner) and replaces it with a function (getUserIdsAndEmailsFromTeamIds) that accepts arbitrary teamIds without verifying the requesting user's role. This allows any authenticated user to enumerate members and emails of any team by providing teamIds, bypassing the previous authorization guard.",
          "suggestion": "Reintroduce a membership condition check that ensures the requesting user is an admin or owner of the specified teams before returning member IDs and emails. Alternatively, validate that the provided teamIds are teams where the user has the required role.",
          "confidence": 0.85,
          "evidence_ids": [
