          "message": "The import of PermissionCheckService from '@calcom/features/pbac/services/permission-check.service' introduces a cross-package dependency from trpc to features, violating the 'Prevent Circular Dependencies Between Core Packages' guideline which states that trpc must not import from features.",
          "suggestion": "Move the permission check logic to a shared package that both trpc and features can depend on, or refactor to avoid the dependency.",
